            "headline": "Mandalay Resources had a successful 2024, with record financial performance generating $69 million in free cash flow. Q4 revenue increased by 32% to $66.8 million, cost operating at $1,085 per ounce of gold, and net income of $20.7 million. Full-year revenue hit $240.7 million, cash flow reached $112.7 million, and net income was $47.8 million. The company aims to continue its success in 2025 with planned investments and production targets.",
